{"_id":"sr3e-prog-0003","name":"Armor","type":"program","img":"icons/svg/network.svg","system":{"name":"Armor","type":"Program","category":"Operational","rating":0,"sizeMp":0,"multiplier":3,"degradable":true,"description":"\u003cp\u003eMay be used to soak Overload Damage. Instead of applying damage to Matrix Condition Monitor, degrade Armor on a point-for-point basis.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSoak Type:\u003c/strong\u003e Overload\u003c/p\u003e","associatedPrompt":"Attack an Icon (Defense)","effect":"Damage Soak"}}
{"_id":"sr3e-prog-0004","name":"Attack","type":"program","img":"icons/svg/network.svg","system":{"name":"Attack","type":"Program","category":"Combat","rating":0,"sizeMp":0,"multiplier":0,"degradable":false,"description":"\u003cp\u003eOperational combat program designed to inflict damage upon other icons.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eVariants:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eLight Overload (×2)\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eModerate Overload (×3)\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eSevere Overload (×4)\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eDeadly Overload (×5)\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eNosebleed — Light Biofeedback (×5)\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eBlackout — Moderate Biofeedback (×10)\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eKilljoy — Severe Biofeedback (×15)\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eBlack Hammer — Deadly Biofeedback (×20)\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e","associatedPrompt":"Attack an Icon","effect":"Damage"}}
